  <brief_title>Rate of Non-copers to Non-surgical ACL Treatment After 3 Months of Rehabilitation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Rate of Non-copers to Non-surgical ACL Treatment After 3 Months of Rehabilitation - a Prospective Cohort Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
