  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim is to determine the sensitivity and specificity of a screening tool to identify&#xD;
      patients who undergo ACL reconstruction (non-copers) after 3 months of standard&#xD;
      rehabilitation following an anterior Cruciate ligament (ACL) injury.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
